    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Dear loyal subject, I received your report. You have uncovered a plot none could predict. Akechi Mitsuhide is a traitor to us all, even Nobunaga."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "However, it matters little whether Mitsuhide works of his own accord. Both he and Nobunaga must be stopped."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Do not let this new development faze your resolve. You must keep your focus to unravel the enemy's plan."
      },
      "3": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Haruaki and I will deal with the confusion in Momijigaoka. You focus on saving the world. - Sakuno"
      },
